in the top 500 in the exam]

365
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:37,540
[Own 10 Rolls-Royces]

366
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:41,180
[I want to get into a good university]

367
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,750
