398
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:50,670
I'm not messing with you.

399
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:51,690
Trust me.

400
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,640
It's not like you can't achieve

401
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:55,480
